You always rest assured your funds are safely secured within your own access 100% of the time the bot is operating. You can cancel the bot at anytime to relocate your settings or coin preferences! Users that purchase this package will gain access to the trading bot for one month to allow initial testing within the community, as well as provide feedback for growth/feature implementation towards public launch coming up. By purchasing this 1 month ALPHA lease option, you will receive $100 discount on your next purchase for $999.00/1 year leasing , therefore only being charged $899.00/1year  After the month has completed we will gather customer feedback and upgrade the bot accordingly to better suite their needs We will be adding over 15 new indicators based on the submitted feedback after the intital launch period! Author: d@anksignals
Title: [ANN][]DANK SIGNALS- Revolutionizing Crypto Education and trading
Body: If you click any trade analysis photo in the group - you wll quickly see it is engaged on Bittrex at the moment. We have plans to expand to signal Binance in the near future once up and fully running  Great mention regarding the token supply. Actually, our token supply is perfect for our economics of development, This is a very effective supply amount  based how we have modelled our development. Our initial supply will be 1,000,000,000 and will grow as new members join the platform and new tokens are needed. The problem with platforms in the past, is there is not enough token liquidity to stay afloat once functioning and to be able to successfully manage coin flow when new members come on board once the platform has launched. Once the initial investors input their tokens to the lending platform or being staking/holding that they purchased from the ICO for long term gains, the liquid supply will be drastically reduced during the investment vesting period.
